      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a solid choice for someone looking for reliable transportation on a budget. While the engine and transmission are functional, the car shows noticeable signs of wear, including some cosmetic blemishes on the exterior and interior surfaces. It has been driven regularly and may require some minor maintenance or cosmetic touch-ups in the near future to bring it back to its best. Overall, it's a dependable car that gets the job done without the premium price tag of a newer model.",
