    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition and presents exactly as it did the day it rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like finish, and the interior is pristine, showing no signs of wear on the upholstery or controls. Mechanically, it is perfect, having been meticulously maintained and stored in a climate-controlled environment. This is a rare opportunity to own a truly showroom-quality example that will satisfy even the most discerning collector.",
